CHEROKEE FUEL COMPANY v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 43289] [89 C. Cls. 279;

309 U. S. —]

Government contract; cancellation; schedule of delivery calls; termination of contract. Petition dismissed May 29, *6841939; plaintiff’s motion for new trial overruled October 2, 1939.

Petition for writ of certiorari denied by the Supreme Court January 29, 1940.
